&gt;&gt; You

00:06:39.960 --> 00:06:41.790
know, to be honest, I haven't thought about

00:06:41.790 --> 00:06:45.120
it too much, because Again, that fantasy play

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:49.340
of, you know, finding my biological parents. Like,

